nodes.text: A female individual served as Supreme Chancellor of the Galactic Republic around 85 BBY.

During the Supreme Chancellor's time in office, Jedi Master Lene Kostana informed Senator Tavetti of a potential threat to his homeworld of Protobranch after her apprentice Sifo-Dyas experienced a Force vision foretelling it. In response, Tavetti promised to speak to the Chancellor in the hopes that she would order the Jedi High Council to investigate.
